fields.name: Gibson USA Les Paul Standard '50s Faded Electric Guitar in Vintage Honey Burst
fields.description: Sporting a satin nitrocellulose lacquer finish, the Les Paul Standard 50s Faded has the look and feel of a well-loved vintage instrument. Built on the tried and tested foundation of a solid Mahogany body and AA figured Maple top, it is dynamic and resonant with sustain for days. The Mahogany neck has a rounded 50s-style profile, adding to the vintage feel, and is topped with a silky smooth Rosewood fingerboard. At the heart of the Les Paul is a set of double-black, open-coil Burstbucker pickups, with a Burstbucker 1 in the neck and Burstbucker 2 in the bridge. Other premium appointments include an ABR-1 Tune-O-Matic bridge, vintage deluxe tuners, Orange Drop capacitors and a hardshell case.

fields.name: Boss Katana 50 Gen 3 50w Guitar Amp Combo
fields.description: The BOSS KATANA Gen 3 range is here with another amp character, evolved tube logic, improved tone storage and an updated app to once again take its spot as the go-to amplifier for the modern guitarist. This amplifier is a compact 50-watt combo with a custom 12-inch speaker with evolved Tube Logic sound, 12 amp characters, onboard BOSS effects, an incredible app and more. With the additon of the BOSS BT-DUAL Blueooth Adapter, you can literally remote edit your settings and playback from your phone!

fields.name: Fender CD-60SCE All-Mahogany Dreadnought Electro Acoustic Guitar in Natural
fields.description: The Fender CD-60SCE combines comfortable playability, great tone, and built-in Fishman electronics into one affordable acoustic guitar, ideal for those looking to start their acoustic guitar playing journey

fields.name: Boss SD-1 Super Overdrive Pedal
fields.description: A simple yet effective overdrive powering smooth rock tones synonymous with classic overdriven amps. As you'd expect then, the Boss SD-1 pedal is particularly effective for blues and rock! Overdrive that doesn't oversaturate or overcompress leaving the dynamics and nuances of your playing intact.
